OL,3,CEx-BBC correspondent in Africa says
OL,4,Cfirst reaction to Live Aid was 'real
OL,5,Canger'
OL,7,FMichael Buerk, a journalist who
OL,8,Freported on the Ethiopian famine in
OL,9,F1984, has said his initial reaction to
OL,10,Fthe Live Aid concerts, which raised
OL,11,Ffunds for the crisis, "was real anger".
OL,13,FThe event, organised by musicians Bob
OL,14,FGeldof and Midge Ure, which was held
OL,15,Fat London's Wembley Stadium and John F
OL,16,FKennedy Stadium in the US, is
OL,17,Fcelebrating its 40th anniversary.
