OL,3,CEx-BBC correspondent in Africa says
OL,4,Cfirst reaction to Live Aid was 'real
OL,5,Canger'
OL,7,FThe concerts raised millions of
OL,8,Fpounds, but some have criticised its
OL,9,Fportrayal of Africa, with Geldof
OL,10,Frejecting the idea that he is a "white
OL,11,Fsaviour" due to his charity work.
OL,13,FVeteran broadcaster Buerk, 79, who was
OL,14,Fa presenter on the BBC's Ten O'Clock
OL,15,FNews, now known as BBC News At Ten,
OL,16,Fbrought the shocking plight of famine-
OL,17,Fhit Ethiopia to the world in 1984 with
OL,18,Fhis heart-rending reports.
