OL,3,CEx-BBC correspondent in Africa says
OL,4,Cfirst reaction to Live Aid was 'real
OL,5,Canger'
OL,7,FSpeaking to Greatest Hits Radio, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "My first reaction (to Live Aid)
OL,9,Fwas real anger that I thought
OL,10,Fsuperficial, grandstanding pop singers
OL,11,Fwere riding on the back of these
OL,12,Fpeople who I felt very protective of.
OL,14,F"I didn't watch it and in fact on the
OL,15,Fafternoon of Live Aid I was in a black
OL,16,Ftownship just to the east of
OL,17,FJohannesburg being tear gassed... also
OL,18,Fof course South Africa was one of the
OL,19,Fvery, very few countries that didn't
OL,20,Fshow it."
