OL,3,CEx-BBC correspondent in Africa says
OL,4,Cfirst reaction to Live Aid was 'real
OL,5,Canger'
OL,7,FSpeaking about the famine in Ethiopia,
OL,8,Fhe added: "I'd never seen anything
OL,9,Flike this, there was a lot of drought
OL,10,Fand a lot of hunger in South Africa in
OL,11,Fthe 1980s (but) what we hadn't seen
OL,12,Fwas famine, death at that kind of
OL,13,Fscale before...
