OL,3,CEx-BBC correspondent in Africa says
OL,4,Cfirst reaction to Live Aid was 'real
OL,5,Canger'
OL,7,F"I was very concerned when I got back
OL,8,Fto Nairobi about how to tell the story
OL,9,Fbecause I was there I was not just
OL,10,Fseeing it and hearing it but smelling
OL,11,Fit; and I wondered what the reaction
OL,12,Fwould be for people who would be
OL,13,Fsitting and watching it in the comfort
OL,14,Fof their own homes, cup of tea, glass
OL,15,Fof beer or something and it's just on
OL,16,Fin two dimensions in the corner of the
OL,17,Fliving room."
